## Change Type Reference

| Type | Meaning |
|------|---------|
| `value_added` | New coded domain value |
| `value_removed` | Coded domain value deleted |
| `attribute_added` | New column added to a class |
| `attribute_removed` | Column removed from a class |
| `class_added` | New table introduced |
| `class_removed` | Table deleted |
| `domain_source_changed` | Attribute relinked to different domain source (e.g. inline → KE) |
| `hierarchy_changed` | Values reorganized without explicit add/remove list |
| `content_cleared` | Data cleared, schema structure unchanged |
| `class_content_removed` | Features removed from a class |
| `data_fill` | Gap-filling operation on existing schema |
| `attribute_relinked` | Attribute reconnected to a different coded domain |
